content.raw: Ah, no. I never intended for that to be added, but my text editor did act a bit odd when I was updating other docstrings in this class. I use `AutoDocstring` with SublimeText3, which usually just scans an undocumented method and creates a formatted placeholder docstring, but it appears to do more than that.
